<b:comment>Pengaturan Charset</b:comment> <meta content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' http-equiv='Content-Type'/>
<b:comment>Deskripsi dan SEO</b:comment> <b:if cond='data:blog.metaDescription'> <meta expr:content='data:blog.metaDescription' name='description'/> <meta expr:content='data:blog.metaDescription' property='og:description'/> <meta expr:content='data:blog.metaDescription' name='twitter:description'/> <b:else/> <meta expr:content='data:view.title' name='description'/> <meta expr:content='data:view.title' property='og:description'/> <meta expr:content='data:view.title' name='twitter:description'/> </b:if>
<b:comment>Judul Halaman</b:comment> <b:if cond='data:view.isHomepage or (data:view.isSearch and !data:view.isLabelSearch and !data:blog.searchQuery)'> <title><data:view.title.escaped/></title> <meta expr:content='data:view.title' property='og:title'/> <meta expr:content='data:view.title' property='og:image:alt'/> <meta expr:content='data:view.title' name='twitter:title'/> <meta expr:content='data:view.title' name='twitter:image:alt'/> <b:elseif cond='data:view.isSingleItem or data:view.isSearch or data:view.isArchive'/> <title><data:blog.pageName/> - <data:blog.title/></title> <meta expr:content='data:blog.pageName + " - " + data:blog.title' property='og:title'/> <meta expr:content='data:blog.pageName + " - " + data:blog.title' property='og:image:alt'/> <meta expr:content='data:blog.pageName + " - " + data:blog.title' name='twitter:title'/> <meta expr:content='data:blog.pageName + " - " + data:blog.title' name='twitter:image:alt'/> <b:elseif cond='data:view.isError'/> <title>Page Not Found - <data:blog.title/></title> <meta expr:content='"Page Not Found - " + data:blog.title' property='og:title'/> <meta expr:content='"Page Not Found - " + data:blog.title' property='og:image:alt'/> <meta expr:content='"Page Not Found - " + data:blog.title' name='twitter:title'/> <meta expr:content='"Page Not Found - " + data:blog.title' name='twitter:image:alt'/> <b:else/> <title><data:view.title/></title> <meta expr:content='data:view.title' property='og:title'/> <b:comment>Gambar Alt untuk Sosial Media</b:comment> <meta expr:content='data:view.title' property='og:image:alt'/> <meta expr:content='data:view.title' name='twitter:title'/> <meta expr:content='data:view.title' name='twitter:image:alt'/> </b:if>
<b:comment>Meta Sosial Media Tambahan</b:comment> <meta content='MyBerkas' property='og:site_name'/> <meta content='article' property='og:type'/> <meta content='id_ID' property='og:locale'/> <meta content='en_US' property='og:locale:alternate'/> <meta content='en_GB' property='og:locale:alternate'/> <meta content='summary_large_image' name='twitter:card'/>

<b:comment>OpenID dan Canonical Link</b:comment> <link expr:href='data:blog.url.canonical' rel='canonical'/> <link expr:href='data:blog.url.canonical' hreflang='x-default' rel='alternate'/> <meta expr:content='data:blog.url.canonical' property='og:url'/>
<b:comment>Pengaturan OpenID</b:comment> <link href='https://www.blogger.com/openid-server.g' rel='openid.server'/> <link expr:href='data:blog.homepageUrl.canonical' rel='openid.delegate'/>

<script>
  let url = `myblog.com/search?genres=Action&genres=Adventure&year=2024&season=Fall`;

  let custom_post = new BloggerScript({
    noImage: noThumbnail_Vertikal,
    sizeImage: 's320'
  });

  const aggregateAndFilterResults = (responses, filterLabels) => {
    let allEntries = [];
    responses.forEach(response => {
      let entries = custom_post.getFeed(response);
      allEntries.push(...entries); // Menambahkan semua entri ke array tunggal
    });

    // Menghapus duplikat berdasarkan 'id'
    let uniqueEntries = allEntries.reduce((acc, current) => {
      if (!acc.some(item => item.id === current.id)) {
        acc.push(current);
      }
      return acc;
    }, []);

    // Filter hasil dengan label yang ditentukan
    const filteredEntries = uniqueEntries.filter(item => 
      filterLabels.some(label => item.label.includes(label))
    );

    console.log(filterLabels);

    console.log('Final filtered array:', filteredEntries); // Menampilkan array hasil filter di konsol
    return filteredEntries;
  };

  const run_custom_post = () => {
    // Extracting label values from the URL
    let params = new URLSearchParams(url.split('?')[1]);
    let labels = [];

    if (params.has('genres')) {
      labels.push(...params.getAll('genres'));
    }
    if (params.has('year')) {
      labels.push(params.get('year'));
    }
    if (params.has('season')) {
      labels.push(params.get('season'));
    }

    // Removing duplicates in the labels array
    let uniqueLabels = [...new Set(labels)];

    console.log(uniqueLabels);

    // Running requests for each unique label
    let promises = uniqueLabels.map(label_name => {
      return new Promise((resolve, reject) => {
        custom_post.xhr(`/feeds/posts/default/-/${label_name}?alt=json-in-script&max-results=150`, (e) => {
          resolve(e);
        });
      });
    });

    // Handling the aggregation and filtering of results
    Promise.all(promises).then(responses => {
      aggregateAndFilterResults(responses, uniqueLabels); // Menggabungkan dan memfilter hasil
    }).catch(err => {
      console.error('Error fetching posts:', err);
    });
  };

  document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', () => {
    run_custom_post();
  });
</script>
